{"id":2946,"date":"2022-04-04T19:38:38","date_gmt":"2022-04-04T12:38:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/?p=1256"},"modified":"2022-04-04T19:38:38","modified_gmt":"2022-04-04T12:38:38","slug":"nen-deo-nhan-vao-ngon-nao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/nen-deo-nhan-vao-ngon-nao\/","title":{"rendered":"N\u00caN \u0110EO NH\u1eaaN V\u00c0O NG\u00d3N N\u00c0O?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"\" dir=\"auto\">\n<div id=\"jsc_c_1w\" class=\"ecm0bbzt hv4rvrfc ihqw7lf3 dati1w0a\" data-ad-comet-preview=\"message\" data-ad-preview=\"message\">\n<div class=\"j83agx80 cbu4d94t ew0dbk1b irj2b8pg\">\n<div class=\"qzhwtbm6 knvmm38d\">\n<div class=\"kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Th\u1eddi trang d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eabn \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qua \u0111i. Phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn \u0111ang thay \u0111\u1ed5i, kim lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra, nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang tr\u00ed, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u1eadt trang s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong su\u1ed1t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a nh\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i. Theo th\u1eddi gian, vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecdn \u0111eo nh\u1eabn \u1edf ng\u00f3n tay n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c: th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 do ti\u1ec1m th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0a ra, v\u00e0 n\u00f3 bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ch\u00fang ta h\u01a1n ch\u00ednh ch\u00fang ta. May m\u1eafn thay, kinh nghi\u1ec7m m\u00e0 nh\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng t\u1ecf nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi, v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y nay ch\u00fang ta bi\u1ebft \u00fd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c \u0111eo nh\u1eabn \u1edf m\u1ed9t ng\u00f3n tay n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. Ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">V\u00d2NG NG\u00d3N TAY C\u00c1I.<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/nhan-ca-chep-hoa-rong-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3224 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/nhan-ca-chep-hoa-rong-1.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eabn C\u00e1 Ch\u00e9p H\u00f3a R\u1ed3ng (1)\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/nhan-ca-chep-hoa-rong-1.jpg 750w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/nhan-ca-chep-hoa-rong-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/nhan-ca-chep-hoa-rong-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/nhan-ca-chep-hoa-rong-1-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/nhan-ca-chep-hoa-rong-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Ng\u00f3n tay c\u00e1i c\u00f3 t\u00ean g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ng\u00f3n tay c\u1ee7a Mars &#8211; v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn tranh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi La M\u00e3 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo thuy\u1ebft b\u00e0n tay tin r\u1eb1ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f3n tay c\u00e1i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m cho nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, t\u01b0 duy logic v\u00e0 \u00fd ch\u00ed m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7n \u0111eo nh\u1eabn \u1edf ng\u00f3n c\u00e1i: \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ed3i sinh n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ee9a trong n\u00f3 v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u00edch nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, th\u00ec h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh lam ho\u1eb7c xanh l\u1ee5c lam cho ng\u00f3n tay c\u00e1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 do c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 hung h\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a sao H\u1ecfa &#8211; \u200b\u200bn\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<h3 dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-Nam-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2443\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-Nam-1.jpg\" alt=\"Nhan Nam 1.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-Nam-1.jpg 500w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-Nam-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-Nam-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-Nam-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/a><\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn \u1edf ng\u00f3n tr\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c, ng\u00f3n tr\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a M\u1ed9c tinh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ed7i l\u1ea1c nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed nh\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn tr\u00ean ng\u00f3n tr\u1ecf v\u00e0 do \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111eo nh\u1eabn tr\u00ean ch\u00fang. Trong ch\u00e2n dung c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n c\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang nh\u01b0 Guy Julius Caesar, Henry VIII, Elizabeth I, Ivan B\u1ea1o ch\u00faa, H\u1ed3ng y Richelieu, ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p \u201cchi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c\u201d.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 trang s\u1ee9c \u1edf ng\u00f3n tr\u1ecf: nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 \u00e1i th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdn ng\u00f3n tr\u1ecf c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n tay tr\u00e1i, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch ki\u00eau h\u00e3nh v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd l\u1ea1i th\u00edch tay ph\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111eo nh\u1eabn \u1edf ng\u00f3n tr\u1ecf: \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a sao M\u1ed9c v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt s\u1ef1 nh\u00fat nh\u00e1t qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">NH\u1eaaN TR\u00caN NG\u00d3N GI\u1eeeA<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Nhan-da-thien-nhien-cao-cap-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3460 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Nhan-da-thien-nhien-cao-cap-4.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 Thi\u00ean Nhi\u00ean Cao C\u1ea5p (4)\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Nhan-da-thien-nhien-cao-cap-4.jpg 750w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Nhan-da-thien-nhien-cao-cap-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Nhan-da-thien-nhien-cao-cap-4-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Nhan-da-thien-nhien-cao-cap-4-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Nhan-da-thien-nhien-cao-cap-4-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Tr\u00ean ng\u00f3n gi\u1eefa, nh\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo &#8211; d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 n\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 \u00edch. Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u00f3n tay n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 y\u00ean t\u00e2m; c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 chi\u00eam tinh h\u1ecdc n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a sao Th\u1ed5, h\u00e0nh tinh duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1ea3o tr\u1ee3 cho ng\u00f3n gi\u1eefa. Th\u1eadt ra ng\u00f3n gi\u1eefa c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111eo nh\u1eabn v\u00ec n\u00f3 n\u1eb1m ch\u00ednh gi\u1eefa b\u00e0n tay \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng trang s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111eo nh\u1eabn gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u1edf ng\u00f3n n\u00e0y, th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 h\u1ebft v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xung quanh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh an cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">NH\u1eaaN TR\u00caN NG\u00d3N \u00c1P \u00daT<\/h3>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-bac-da-peridot-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3529 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-bac-da-peridot-3.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eabn B\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e1 Peridot (3)\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-bac-da-peridot-3.jpg 750w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-bac-da-peridot-3-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-bac-da-peridot-3-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-bac-da-peridot-3-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-bac-da-peridot-3-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/><\/a><\/h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo \u1edf ng\u00f3n \u00e1p \u00fat, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y: \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u00f3n \u0111eo nh\u1eabn k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i tim v\u00e0 M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi &#8211; nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 c\u1edb m\u00e0 nh\u1eabn c\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh ng\u00f3n tay n\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea1i, n\u01a1i s\u1ef1 s\u00f9ng b\u00e1i M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u1edf m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u1eabn c\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u1ec5 \u0111\u00ednh h\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo tr\u00ean tay kh\u00e1c nhau: \u0111\u1ee9c tin C\u00f4ng gi\u00e1o quy \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111eo ch\u00fang b\u00ean tay tr\u00e1i, v\u00e0 Ch\u00ednh th\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1o &#8211; b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i. N\u00f3i chung, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1ecf, b\u1edfi v\u00ec trong m\u1ecdi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Khi ch\u1ecdn trang s\u1ee9c cho ng\u00f3n \u00e1p \u00fat, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn quan h\u1ec7 h\u00f4n nh\u00e2n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0ng, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 carnelian, h\u1ed3ng l\u1ef1u, ruby, h\u1ed5 ph\u00e1ch, sapphire v\u00e0ng, citrine&#8230; \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a trang tr\u00ed v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1ng, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 vui v\u1ebb. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n thu h\u00fat b\u00f9a y\u00eau th\u00ec h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u00ednh ng\u1ecdc trai tr\u1eafng &#8211; bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh trong s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 thu\u1ea7n khi\u1ebft.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">NH\u1eaaN TR\u00caN NG\u00d3N \u00daT<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2429\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1.jpg\" alt=\"Nhan Nu 21 1.jpg\" width=\"794\" height=\"794\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1.jpg 794w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Nhan-nu-21-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-nam-vang-14k-da-citrine-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3534\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-nam-vang-14k-da-citrine-3.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eabn Nam V\u00e0ng 14k \u0111\u00e1 Citrine (3)\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-nam-vang-14k-da-citrine-3.jpg 750w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-nam-vang-14k-da-citrine-3-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-nam-vang-14k-da-citrine-3-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-nam-vang-14k-da-citrine-3-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/nhan-nam-vang-14k-da-citrine-3-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn \u1edf ng\u00f3n \u00fat, nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t quy lu\u1eadt, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c doanh nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u01b0a th\u00edch, b\u1edfi v\u00ec ng\u00f3n tay n\u00e0y g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi sao Th\u1ee7y &#8211; v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn, ma thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 h\u00f9ng bi\u1ec7n. Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tinh th\u1ea7n trong s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n kinh doanh, th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f3n \u00fat. Chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn \u1edf ng\u00f3n \u00fat c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3: h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 bay b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c tinh t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 t\u00e0i h\u00f9ng bi\u1ec7n xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 s\u00e1ng, th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, ngay c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 trang s\u1ee9c nh\u1ecf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u00f3 v\u00e0 n\u00f3i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1ch \u0111eo n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"jsc_c_1x\" class=\"l9j0dhe7\">\n<div class=\"l9j0dhe7\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"l9j0dhe7\">\n<div class=\"l9j0dhe7\">\n<div class=\"ni8dbmo4 stjgntxs pmk7jnqg\">\n<div class=\"stjgntxs ni8dbmo4\">\n<div class=\"do00u71z ni8dbmo4 stjgntxs l9j0dhe7\">\n<div class=\"pmk7jnqg kr520xx4\"><img class=\"i09qtzwb n7fi1qx3 datstx6m pmk7jnqg j9ispegn kr520xx4 k4urcfbm\" src=\"https:\/\/scontent.fsgn2-3.fna.fbcdn.net\/v\/t1.6435-9\/p180x540\/159510059_2122957211173737_6494688418108323506_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=1-5&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=HbnzDogh6VwAX_TFs2k&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fsgn2-3.fna&amp;oh=0e2a31819e28394e5c8be9cc90987376&amp;oe=6166B5F2\" alt=\"\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"hzruof5a opwvks06 linmgsc8 kr520xx4 j9ispegn pmk7jnqg n7fi1qx3 rq0escxv i09qtzwb\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"n00je7tq arfg74bv qs9ysxi8 k77z8yql i09qtzwb n7fi1qx3 b5wmifdl hzruof5a pmk7jnqg j9ispegn kr520xx4 c5ndavph art1omkt ot9fgl3s\" data-visualcompletion=\"ignore\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"ni8dbmo4 stjgntxs pmk7jnqg\">\n<div class=\"stjgntxs ni8dbmo4\">\n<div class=\"do00u71z ni8dbmo4 stjgntxs l9j0dhe7\">\n<div class=\"pmk7jnqg kr520xx4\"><img class=\"i09qtzwb n7fi1qx3 datstx6m pmk7jnqg j9ispegn kr520xx4 k4urcfbm\" src=\"https:\/\/scontent.fsgn2-4.fna.fbcdn.net\/v\/t1.6435-9\/p600x600\/159939269_2122957251173733_7367551471107664282_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=1-5&amp;_nc_sid=b9115d&amp;_nc_ohc=Co4-28Fa5zMAX9OL7P8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fsgn2-4.fna&amp;oh=ed111722bc6fa4c9b972fceeb8978a39&amp;oe=6166E0A2\" alt=\"\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"hzruof5a opwvks06 linmgsc8 kr520xx4 j9ispegn pmk7jnqg n7fi1qx3 rq0escxv i09qtzwb\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u1eddi trang d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eabn \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qua \u0111i. Phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn \u0111ang thay \u0111\u1ed5i, kim lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra, nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang tr\u00ed, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n chi\u1ebfc nh\u1eabn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u1eadt &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2032,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[176,179],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2946"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2946"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2946\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3565,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2946\/revisions\/3565"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2032"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2946"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2946"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2946"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}